#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an5.116"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an5.116:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 5 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 5 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.116:0.2"
msgid "12. Andhakavindavagga "
msgstr "12. At Andhakavinda "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: vaṇṇasuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "an5.116:0.3"
msgid "116. Vaṇṇanāsutta "
msgstr "116. Praise "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "an5.116:1.1"
msgid "“Pañcahi, bhikkhave, dhammehi samannāgatā bhikkhunī yathābhataṃ nikkhittā evaṃ niraye. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, a nun with five qualities is cast down to hell. "

msgctxt "an5.116:1.2"
msgid "Katamehi pañcahi? "
msgstr "What five? "

msgctxt "an5.116:1.3"
msgid "Ananuvicca apariyogāhetvā avaṇṇārahassa vaṇṇaṃ bhāsati, "
msgstr "Without examining or scrutinizing, she praises those deserving of criticism, "

msgctxt "an5.116:1.4"
msgid "ananuvicca apariyogāhetvā vaṇṇārahassa avaṇṇaṃ bhāsati, "
msgstr "and criticizes those deserving of praise. "

msgctxt "an5.116:1.5"
msgid "ananuvicca apariyogāhetvā appasādanīye ṭhāne pasādaṃ upadaṃseti, "
msgstr "She arouses faith in things that are dubious, "

msgctxt "an5.116:1.6"
msgid "ananuvicca apariyogāhetvā pasādanīye ṭhāne appasādaṃ upadaṃseti, "
msgstr "and doesn’t arouse faith in things that are inspiring. "

msgctxt "an5.116:1.7"
msgid "saddhādeyyaṃ vinipāteti. "
msgstr "And she wastes gifts given in faith. "

msgctxt "an5.116:1.8"
msgid "Imehi kho, bhikkhave, pañcahi dhammehi samannāgatā bhikkhunī yathābhataṃ nikkhittā evaṃ niraye. "
msgstr "A nun with these five qualities is cast down to hell. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli3.140, sc2
msgctxt "an5.116:2.1"
msgid "Pañcahi, bhikkhave, dhammehi samannāgatā bhikkhunī yathābhataṃ nikkhittā evaṃ sagge. "
msgstr "A nun with five qualities is raised up to heaven. "

msgctxt "an5.116:2.2"
msgid "Katamehi pañcahi? "
msgstr "What five? "

msgctxt "an5.116:2.3"
msgid "Anuvicca pariyogāhetvā avaṇṇārahassa avaṇṇaṃ bhāsati, "
msgstr "After examining and scrutinizing, she criticizes those deserving of criticism, "

msgctxt "an5.116:2.4"
msgid "anuvicca pariyogāhetvā vaṇṇārahassa vaṇṇaṃ bhāsati, "
msgstr "and praises those deserving of praise. "

msgctxt "an5.116:2.5"
msgid "anuvicca pariyogāhetvā appasādanīye ṭhāne appasādaṃ upadaṃseti, "
msgstr "She doesn’t arouse faith in things that are dubious, "

msgctxt "an5.116:2.6"
msgid "anuvicca pariyogāhetvā pasādanīye ṭhāne pasādaṃ upadaṃseti, "
msgstr "and does arouse faith in things that are inspiring. "

msgctxt "an5.116:2.7"
msgid "saddhādeyyaṃ na vinipāteti. "
msgstr "And she doesn’t waste gifts given in faith. "

msgctxt "an5.116:2.8"
msgid "Imehi kho, bhikkhave, pañcahi dhammehi samannāgatā bhikkhunī yathābhataṃ nikkhittā evaṃ sagge”ti. "
msgstr "A nun with these five qualities is raised up to heaven.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an5.116:2.9"
msgid "Chaṭṭhaṃ. "
msgstr ""

